articles.title: America is on the brink of an unemployment fiasco - Business Insider
articles.description: The unemployment rate keeps rising. To prevent the job market from getting worse, the Fed needs to cut interest rates — fast.

articles.author: Matt Lavietes
articles.title: Mother of American missing in Bahamas shielded daughter's trans identity - NBC News
articles.description: The mother of an American woman who went missing in the Bahamas last month while on a monthlong yoga retreat revealed that her daughter is transgender, a detail she said she had withheld out of fear it might negatively affect the search.
